text: "Faded" is a song by Alan Walker with vocals by singer Iselin Solheim. The song was very successful and reached the top 10 in many countries. It is the 21st most viewed video on YouTube, with more than 3.6 billion views. "Faded" is also the 48th most streamed song on Spotify, with more than 2 billion streams. Category:2015 songs
title: Faded (Alan Walker song)
